Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 ne suka saurari sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 ne suka saurari shaidar da aka ba da ranar Talata ta Alƙali Brett Kavanaugh da kuma ta Christine Blasey Ford, wata mata da ta yi masa zargin yin lalata da ya faru a shekara ta 1990 kuma an yi ta ta ba da shaida a wurare shida dabam dabam.
A lokaci guda, hargitsi na siyasa ya ci gaba, kuma gidajen talabijin sun yi watsi da jadawalin su na yin labarai na yau da kullum a ranar Jumma'a: Jeff Flake, wani ɗan majalisar dattijai na Arizona, ya gabatar da wani shiri don FBI ta bincika zargin na mako guda.
Ford ta gaya wa Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya sha giya da kuma ƙoƙarin sa ta yi ado a lokacin bikin makaranta.
Kavanaugh ya ba da shaida mai ban sha'awa cewa ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Mutane da yawa za su iya kallon wannan shari'ar fiye da miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ba da rahoton cewa sun saurara a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ba da shawarar yin amfani da tashoshin talabijin na CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel, da MSNBC.
Ba a ba da dama ga sauran tashoshin talabijin da suka ba da jawabin ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN, da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma yana da matsala wajen tantance yadda mutane ke sauraronmu a ofisoshinmu.
Don a nuna wannan, wannan rukunin masu sauraro suna da girma kamar na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma na bikin Oscar.
A cewar Nielsen, yawancin mutane sun kalli wannan sauraron a kan Fox News Channel, wato miliyan 5.69 kuma masu saka idanu a wannan jerin sun amince da na Kavanaugh.
A lokacin, ABC ta yi nasara a matsayi na biyu, inda ta samu masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS na da miliyan 3.1 da NBC na da miliyan 2.94, MSNBC na da miliyan 2.89 da CNN na da miliyan 2.52, a cewar Nielsen.
Bayan shari'ar, mutane sun yi murna sosai.
