Amirka ta yi nasara a wasanni huɗu na gasar, ta ci wasanni biyu amma ba ta samu nasara ba.
Jim Fury ya bukaci maki takwas daga wasannin da aka buga a ranar Lahadi don ya ci gaba da cin kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon sabon dan wasan Turai da ya ci maki hudu a jere, kuma shi da Molinari, wanda ya dauki sunan mai suna Molliwood bayan babban karshen mako, su ne kawai biyu da suka ci maki hudu daga wasanninsu na farko a tarihin Ryder Bikers.
Bayan sun ci Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan hudu, sun nuna babban haɗin kai kuma sun ci Woods da kuma dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau 5-4.
Woods, wanda ya yi nasara a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna basirarsa a wasu lokatai, amma yanzu ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni 19 na 29 a wasan hudu da hudu, kuma a wasanni bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya yi rashin jin daɗi kafin wasan da ya gabata, ya koma wurin abokinsa, Henrik Stenson a wasan da ya yi, inda suka ci Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka 2-1 - na farko da na uku a jerin manyan 'yan wasa a duniya.
Amma, ba a yi nasara sosai a Turai a wannan rana mai sauƙi da ta dace a kudu maso yammacin Paris ba.
Masu cin nasara uku a gasar golf, Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa wa 'yan Amirka maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
