HIV/AIDS: Sin ta ce an samu karuwar kamuwa da cutar ta HIV da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta ce an samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV ko kuma waɗanda suke da cutar.
Hukumomin lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a ƙasar.
An samu sababbin kamuwa da cutar 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kawai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun shafi jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da abin da ya faru a dā.
A dā, cutar HIV ta yi ta yaduwa a wasu sassan ƙasar Sin saboda ba da jini.
A wani taron da aka yi a lardin Yunnan, jami'an kiwon lafiya a kasar Sin sun ce, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar ya sake raguwa zuwa kusan sifili.
Amma, adadin waɗanda suke kamuwa da cutar HIV ko kuma cutar ta ƙonewa ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
Tun daga shekara ta 1997, ba a haramta luwaɗi a kasar Sin ba, amma har yanzu ana nuna bambanci sosai ga LGBT.
Domin dokar hana aure, an kiyasta cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza sun auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne domin rashin kāre haihuwa a waɗannan ma'aurata.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar yin amfani da maganin HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani ɓangare na shirin magance cutar.
