Idan ya cancanta, Washington na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa don hana Rasha samun karfinta a kasuwannin duniya, ciki har da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, a cewar wani rahoto daga Washington Examiner.
