Masu gabatar da kara sun nemi hukuncin kisa na wani dan ta'adda a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a birnin New York sun bukaci a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da yin wani harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane takwas.
An ce Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi hayar motar Home Depot don ya kai hari ga mutane a kan hanyar da ke kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan.
Don a yi amfani da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar game da hukuncin kisa, wadda aka shigar a kotun kudancin New York.
Duk waɗannan tuhumar za su iya kai ga hukuncin kisa, kamar yadda takardar ta ce.
Bayan makonni da yawa bayan harin, kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da wasu mutane 22, ciki har da wasu takwas da ake zargi da kisan kai, wanda ake amfani da shi a lokuta da ake tuhumar ƙungiyoyi masu shirya-tsara.
Masu tuhumar sun ce an yi wani shiri mai zurfi don kai hari, kuma sun bayyana ayyukan Sapiov a matsayin "mai ban tsoro, mai ban tsoro, da kuma rashin ɗabi'a".
An yanke hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov, wanda ya yi wa iyalan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, da kuma iyalansu da kuma abokansa.
Wadanda aka kashe su biyar 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekaru da suka shige ne Jihar New York ta Kudu ta yi amfani da hukuncin kisa a matsayin magani.
An tuhumi wanda ake tuhuma da shi, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe wasu masu sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi biyu, amma a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009, an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a kurkuku.
An yi wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a shekara ta 1953 a kotun New York, bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa domin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War.
A ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953, an kashe su biyu a cikin wutar lantarki.
Saipov, wanda aka haifa a Uzbekistan, bai nuna alamar tuba ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun shari'a.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa wani jami'in bincike cewa abin da ya yi ya sa shi farin ciki.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu ra'ayin harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, kamar yadda ake cewa a cikin tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi ya nuna tutar ISIS a cikin dakin asibitin, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Ya bayyana rashin laifi a gaban shari'ar.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin masu kare Saipov, ya ce sun yi baƙin ciki sosai game da shawarar da masu gabatar da kara suka yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa, yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin da ba a yi masa na rai ba, zai kara wa duk wanda ya yi amfani da wannan lamarin da ya shafi lamarin, "in ji Patton.
A baya, masu kare Saipov sun gaya wa mai gabatar da kara cewa kada a nemi a yi masa hukuncin kisa.
