Dundee Stars sun kara da cewa sun yi rashin nasara a gasar Premier da aka yi a ranar Juma'a a kan Belfast Giants, inda suka ci nasara a wasan da suka biyo baya, 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
A farkon wasan, Giants sun samu ci gaba biyu bayan Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita a wasan da suka buga a gida, amma Dwyer ya ci gaba da buga wa Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita wa Dundee kuma gol biyu daga Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya tabbatar da nasarar su.
Wannan shi ne wasan na uku da Adam Keefe ya yi a gasar Premier, amma ya ci Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a.
Wannan shi ne wasan hudu da aka buga tsakanin kungiyoyin a kakar wasa, kuma Giants sun lashe wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya ci gaba da ci a minti na hudu da misalin karfe 3.35 na yamma, bayan da Kendall McFaull ya yi masa baftisma.
Daga nan sai ya kasance da yawa a cikin minti na farko da Sullivan ya koma gida a wasan lokacin da 1: 10 na wasan ya nuna kuma Cownie ya daidaita bayan da aka gabatar da shi daga Matt Marquardt a minti na goma sha biyar.
Dwyer ya sa Giants suka yi nasara a wasan da ya ci gaba da buga a wasan a ƙarshen wasan farko.
Ƙungiyar ta ci gaba da ƙarfafawa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa a raga a minti na 27 na wani wasan.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun yi aiki tare kuma sun taimaka wa Nielsen ya kawo Dundee a wasan farko a ƙarshen wasan na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasarar tawagarsa da maki na biyar lokacin da rabin wasan karshe ya ƙare.
A ranar Jumma'a, 'yan Giants da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu na karshe, za su yi wa Milton Keynes wasa na gaba.
